{"id":659313,"date":[{"year":1983,"month":9,"day":1}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"教育园地","column":"","genre":"","count":"161","ytitle":"","mtitle":"沐浴着金色的晨曦，仰望着飘拂的五星红旗","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1983\\09\\8391040101.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>沐浴着金色的晨曦，仰望着飘拂的五星红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国妈妈您早，请接受少先队员的敬礼!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1983\\09\\8391040102.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>庄严秀丽的国徽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是祖国妈妈佩戴的胸花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻激励着我们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志在四方，振兴中华!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入8号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1983\\09\\8391040103.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>胸前戴着鲜艳的领巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声伴着跳动的红心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着祖国妈妈指引的方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“前进，前进，前进进!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐裕根　摄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张运来　诗</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>徐裕根,张运来</FONT>"}]}